{
  "texts": [
    "The RSVQA-HR dataset was created from high-resolution orthophoto (HRO) datasets obtained from USGS.",
    "It consists of 10,659 images, with 1,066,316 question-answer pairs.",
    "RSVQA-HR dataset is divided into training, validation, test set 1, and test set 2.",
    "In the evaluation of zero-shot VQA, test set 2 is adopted for evaluating the model's robustness to diverse locations.",
    "Additionally, following the setting of RSGPT and GeoChat, object counting problems are not included in the computation of metrics for RSVQA-HR."
  ]
}